title: [Yegharren Valley, Clearing]
description: Banks of deep green grass surround a bubbling spring that emerges from the forest floor in the center of a bright clearing between the trees.  Moonlight glints faintly on the water and illuminates the flat, moss-carpeted boulder that extends over the woodland pool.

Banks of deep green grass surround a bubbling spring that emerges from the forest floor in the center of a bright clearing between the trees.  Sunlight sparkles on the water and warms the surface of the flat, moss-carpeted boulder that extends over the woodland pool.
